{"tid":1617432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女兒寫作業睡著！母偷拍出賣　唯美側臉曝光網驚嘆：是IU","createTime":"2019-10-03T19:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T21:11:22.000Z","uid":34643,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6e941d26f43aeb54a1010bd2bb0732c8c234c1","tid":1617432,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:22:40.000Z","msg":"現代的小孩不僅得具備各種才藝，每天更有寫不完的家庭作業，近日就有網友在網路上，曝光了自己女兒寫作業寫到睡著的照片，而唯美的側臉讓不少人看傻了眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/10/03/2164941-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F10%2F03%2F2164941-XXL.jpg&h=9b96f4f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲媽媽在臉書曝光照片出賣自己女兒。（圖／翻攝自爆廢公社）<br />\n<br />\n照片中，原PO女兒趴在桌上，手中還握著鉛筆，從照片中可見正在與學校的數學作業搏鬥，但可愛的睡姿和精緻的五官，讓身為媽媽的原PO哭笑不得的在臉書「爆廢公社」上發文直呼：「寫功課寫到睡著了⋯⋯觀察了十分鐘，筆一直拿的好好的，上學玩的還真累」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/10/03/2164940-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F10%2F03%2F2164940-XXL.jpg&h=0033b89a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲原PO女兒的顏值激似IU。（圖／翻攝自爆廢公社、Instagram）<br />\n<br />\n而照片貼出後，讓網友們驚嘆不已，紛紛留言「好可愛好Q喔」、「妳女兒好可愛」、「快找經紀公司培訓，以後變周子瑜你們後半生就可以靠她了」、「那個睫毛」、「真漂亮的小美女」、「清秀佳人」、「眼睫毛好漂亮」、「不得不說基因真好」、「好像小說封面，好唯美」、「眼睛好好看，這小女孩，以後會一堆人追著跑」、「小朋友睡著都是天使」、「十年計劃是不是該啟動了」、「小孩子皮膚就是好」、「長得好甜」、「根本偶像劇」、「漫畫中的美少女」、「天啊，好唯美的畫面」、「這睫毛好不科學」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/10/03/2164943-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F10%2F03%2F2164943-XXL.jpg&h=77ad6a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲韓國女星IU。（圖／翻攝自Instagram）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/10/03/2164942-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F10%2F03%2F2164942-XXL.jpg&h=ec082605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甚至出現了超多狂喊岳母的網友「大姊我願意等十五年」、「岳母好」、「我可以幫我還不知道在哪的小孩預約嗎」、「我有2個兒子， 可以先排隊嗎」、「岳母好」、「親家母早安」、「大姊我願意等十五年」、「丈母娘妳好」。<br />\n<br />\n更有人發現原PO女兒與韓國知名女星IU有些微的神似「有韓國藝人IU的感覺」、「好漂亮唷，長的好像IU喔」。"},{"pid":"bd4f6f777a3cf8279f05e314fe21340649ebeeab","tid":1617432,"uid":149959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:24:09.000Z","msg":"邊度似<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f8bb2f61e182d42f7d4a95190b4db9196e73d2","tid":1617432,"uid":143288,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:24:12.000Z","msg":"台仔盲撚？"},{"pid":"96ed42335ec6057c940591fe18f93cfdacd1e34b","tid":1617432,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf338896678da2a3917f3bf3e9f39c81d9be1591","tid":1617432,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:56:43.000Z","msg":"個格仔係幾似"},{"pid":"6a9a973a97cc8293c24b09472ceb491c1c8d805c","tid":1617432,"uid":193951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:58:26.000Z","msg":"將我塊面打哂格我都似IU"},{"pid":"36fbefe334d4a89bea5d8a0a6ac69e83d42fda42","tid":1617432,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T21:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10205a4decfd3baf4ef59dbd08985c380feda5fd","tid":1617432,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T21:11:22.000Z","msg":"打晒格林鄭都似啦"}]}